data.description: Take a look at this 4 bedroom, 2 bathroom farmhouse located in West Fork. The home sits on a spacious 2-acre lot, providing plenty of outdoor space for activities. It boasts a  large walkout patio that is perfect for hosting gatherings and entertaining guests. The eat-in kitchen area provides a delightful space for meals while overlooking the backyard. Overall this home offers the perfect balance of farmhouse and rustic charm, making it an excellent choice for anyone seeking a tranquil country lifestyle.
